 42-year-old, Usher and his girlfriend Jenn Goicoechea have announced that they are expecting baby number two. They revealed the exciting news at the 2021 iHeartRadio Music Awards, where Usher was hosting the show. Goicoechea also showed off her baby bump at the 2021 iHeartRadio Music Awards, posing with Usher on the red carpet. The couple welcomed their first child together, Sovereign Bo, in September last year. Congratulations to them